#. type: heading ***
#: configuration.org:1240
#, no-wrap
msgid "Protocol Selection"
msgstr "プロトコルの選択"

#. type: paragraph
#: configuration.org:1242
msgid ""
"The =ssh-ng= protocol is preferred over plain =ssh= because it supports "
"content-addressed derivations and more efficient store path transfers. "
"However, Hydra does not support =ssh-ng= (see [[https://github.com/NixOS/"
"hydra/issues/688][NixOS/hydra#688]]), so the protocol is dynamically "
"selected based on whether Hydra is enabled on the current machine."
msgstr ""
"=ssh-ng= プロトコルはプレーンな =ssh= よりも推奨されます。コンテンツアドレス"
"ドderivationとより効率的なストアパス転送をサポートするためです。ただし、Hydra"
"は =ssh-ng= をサポートしていません（[[https://github.com/NixOS/hydra/issues/"
"688][NixOS/hydra#688]]参照）。そのため、現在のマシンでHydraが有効かどうかに基"
"づいてプロトコルが動的に選択されます。"

#. type: keyword NAME
#: configuration.org:1247
#, no-wrap
msgid "build-machines-let"
msgstr ""

#. type: paragraph in src
#: configuration.org:1249
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"protocol = if (config.services ? hydra && config.services.hydra.enable) then \"ssh\" else \"ssh-ng\";\n"
"inherit (inputs.self.outputs.nixosConfigurations) kilimanjaro serengeti tarangire;\n"
"inherit (inputs.self.outputs.darwinConfigurations) mikumi;"
msgstr ""

