#. type: heading ****
#: modules/configuration.org:339 modules/configuration.org:451
#, no-wrap
msgid "Networking"
msgstr "ネットワーク"

#. type: heading **
#: modules/configuration.org:341
#, no-wrap
msgid "Tailscale"
msgstr "Tailscale"

#. type: paragraph
#: modules/configuration.org:343
msgid ""
"Opinionated Tailscale VPN configuration for NixOS systems. This module "
"provides sensible defaults for running Tailscale with MagicDNS, SSH access, "
"and proper firewall configuration."
msgstr ""
"NixOSシステム向けの独自のTailscale VPN設定です。このモジュールはMagicDNS、SSH"
"アクセス、適切なファイアウォール設定とともにTailscaleを実行するための合理的な"
"デフォルトを提供します。"

#. type: paragraph in src
#: modules/configuration.org:352
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"{ ... }:\n"
"{\n"
"  flake.modules.nixos.tailscale =\n"
"    { config, lib, ... }:\n"
"    let\n"
"      cfg = config.my.services.tailscale;\n"
"    in\n"
"    {\n"
"      <<tailscale-options>>"
msgstr ""

#. type: paragraph in src
#: modules/configuration.org:362
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"      <<tailscale-config>>\n"
"    };\n"
"}"
msgstr ""

#. type: paragraph
#: modules/configuration.org:369
msgid "Module options for controlling Tailscale behavior."
msgstr "Tailscaleの動作を制御するモジュールオプションです。"

#. type: keyword NAME
#: modules/configuration.org:371
#, no-wrap
msgid "tailscale-options"
msgstr ""

#. type: paragraph in src
#: modules/configuration.org:373
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"options.my.services.tailscale = {\n"
"  enable = lib.mkEnableOption \"Tailscale VPN\";"
